T1  - An Integrative Model Of Organizational Trust
AU  - Mayer, Roger C.
AU  - Davis, James H.
AU  - Schoorman, F. David
Y1  - 1995/07/01
PY  - 1995
DA  - 1995/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1995.9508080335
